preinstall (optional):
install python, and the following packages:
pyjq requests configparser

install:
if you trust me, run the following command from the directory you wish to install in:
  curl https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spacerainbow000/Zendesk-SLA-Board/master/install.sh | bash
if you installed dependencies manually, run this instead:
  curl https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spacerainbow000/Zendesk-SLA-Board/master/install.sh | bash -s override

for next release:
add a button in the UI that refreshes the ticket list
have a config file that maps customer tier to a color, and have certain customers of that tier be displayed in that color
